<h3 id="images">Images</h3>

<p>Products can have multiple images to represent them better. To add an image:</p>
<ol>
	<li>Click <strong>Add new image</strong>.</li>
	<li>Click <strong>Browse</strong> to locate imgage on your hard disk drive.</li>
	<li>Click <strong>Upload</strong> to set an image.</li>
</ol>

<ins>
<p>
	Uploaded images will be resized automatically to predefined sizes.
</p>
</ins>

<p class="note">The first uploaded picture is <del>a</del> <ins>the</ins> <strong>Main</strong> image that is displayed in the product list page. It is
also the first image that is displayed in the product details page. All the other pictures <del>are considered
supplemental.</del> will be displayed as enlargeable thumbnails in product detail page.</ins></p>
<img src="image/doc/products/edit/images.bmp">

